---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import phumudzo from "../assets/phumudzo.webp";
---

<Layout>
    <section class="relative min-h-screen">
        <h1 class="text-center pt-40 font-light text-5xl">About Us</h1>
        <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-16 max-w-5xl">
            <!-- Top Section with CEO and How We Started -->
            <div
                class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-center items-start gap-12 mb-16 bg-neutral-800 py-15 rounded-lg shadow"
            >
                <!-- CEO Section -->
                <div class="flex flex-col items-center md:mt-10 w-full md:w-1/3">
                    <Image
                        src={phumudzo}
                        alt="CEO Phumudzo Mhakado"
                        class="w-35 h-35 rounded-full"
                        quality={100}
                    />
                    <div class="mt-4 text-center">
                        <p class="text-2xl font-light">Phumudzo Makhado</p>
                        <p class="text-3xl font-semibold">CEO</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- How We Started Section -->
                <div class="w-full md:w-1/2">
                    <div>
                        <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-6">
                            How We Started
                        </h2>
                        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
                            Founded in 2017 by visionary entrepreneur Phumudzo
                            Makhado in South Africa, Ikoni Capital is a dynamic
                            investment holding company committed to driving
                            transformation and sustainable development across
                            the region. With a diversified investment portfolio
                            spanning agriculture, digital media, student
                            housing, hospitality, and renewable energy, Ikoni
                            Capital stands as a catalyst for progress in South
                            Africa, Southern Africa, and the continent at large.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Philosophy Section -->
            <div class="flex justify-center flex-col text-left">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-2">Mission & Vision</h2>
                <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6 ">
                    At the heart of Ikoni Capital is a steadfast mission: to be
                    a conduit of transformation and development. We are
                    dedicated to nurturing innovative ventures and creating
                    value that transcends conventional boundaries. By investing
                    strategically in sectors that fuel growth and
                    sustainability, we aspire to foster economic development,
                    enhance community well- being, and contribute to a brighter,
                    more resilient future for the regions we serve.
                </p>
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-2">
                    Leadership & Strategic Approach
                </h2>
                <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6 ">
                    Under the guidance of Phumudzo Makhado, Ikoni Capital
                    combines strategic foresight with a passion for innovation.
                    Our investment approach is rooted in thorough market
                    analysis, sustainable practices, and a deep commitment to
                    community empowerment. By partnering with forward-thinking
                    entrepreneurs and industry leaders, we aim to unlock value
                    across our diversified portfolio and contribute meaningfully
                    to the economic transformation of our region.
                </p>
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-2">Future Outlook</h2>
                <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6 ">
                    As we continue to expand our horizons, Ikoni Capital remains
                    dedicated to identifying and nurturing opportunities that
                    drive growth, foster innovation, and promote sustainable
                    development. We are excited about the future and remain
                    steadfast in our commitment to making a positive impact on
                    society and the broader African economy.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>
